@startuml

skinparam nodesep 100
hide methods
hide attributes
hide stereotypes

title Evermind - Domain model

class User
class Creator
class Collection
class Card
class Question
class Answer
class Label
class Search
class Keyword
class ReviewRound

User ..> Search
User *--> Collection
Creator --|> User
Collection o--> "0..*" Card
Collection ..> ReviewRound
Card *--> "1..*" Label
Card *--> Creator
Card *--> Question
Card *--> Answer
Search *--> "1..*" Keyword
Keyword -left-> "0..1" Creator
Keyword --> "0..*" Label
ReviewRound *--> "1..10" Card

@enduml
